            <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m5 12 5 5L20 7"/></svg> Read-only MCP endpoint for Claude, Cursor or any client</li>
